{"_path":"/other/debugging","_dir":"other","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Debugging","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This page contains information on how to identify problems with your installation."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"dns"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DNS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Whilst Postal can verify DNS records on its own, it can be useful to check what the rest of the internet is seeing."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You can make use of "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://whatsmydns.net","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Whats My DNS"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for a quick global check or the "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dig"}]},{"type":"text","value":" command if you have it on a terminal, i.e. "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dig txt yourdomain.com"}]},{"type":"text","value":" or "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dig a yourdomain.com"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"smtp"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SMTP"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The quickest way to ensure the internet can connect to your Postal SMTP is with "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"telnet postal.yourdomain.com 25"}]},{"type":"text","value":". You can proceed to attempt sending a message manually if you are familiar with the raw SMTP commands to further verify your Postal installation is working correctly."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"smtp-ssl"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SMTP SSL"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you aren't sure about whether the SSL certificate you have provided to Postal is set up correctly you can use "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"openssl s_client -connect postal.yourdomain.com:25 -starttls smtp"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to get some information about your certificate from the point of view of SMTP."}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"dns","depth":2,"text":"DNS"},{"id":"smtp","depth":2,"text":"SMTP","children":[{"id":"smtp-ssl","depth":3,"text":"SMTP SSL"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:5.other:3.debugging.md","_source":"content","_file":"5.other/3.debugging.md","_extension":"md"}